---
title: `$date::set()`
description: Create custom date format.
...

~~~ .php.xmp
Date::set($key, $fn = null ($output, $language));
~~~

**Example:**

~~~ .php
Date::set('my_format', function($o, $language) {
    return $o['year'] . '/' . $o['month'] . '/' . $o['day'];
});
~~~

Usage:

~~~ .php
$date = new Date('2016/04/21 16:00:00');

// [1]
echo $date->extract('my_format');

// [2]
echo $date->my_format;
~~~